{"tid":162740,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖] [菲林新仔] 點解我啲相咁唔sharp?","createTime":"2017-03-19T13:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T16:40:03.000Z","uid":88683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89707eb3a849582e33720d0d2c5a9bacc42c7991","tid":162740,"uid":88683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"我唔知係我問題定咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影完啲相點都好唔利 我已經冇將個光圈較到好大 已經係f11 f16果啲都好似好油咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見其他巴打啲菲林相都可以好sharp <br />\n<br />\n雖然有人話玩菲林唔係玩sharp 係玩個味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我想知係我支鏡問題定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用緊smc 50mm 1.4<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/212301_cf94b6e2e708c4c231b3a1bbb8354161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F212301_cf94b6e2e708c4c231b3a1bbb8354161.jpg&h=7cecc090&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eo528d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feo528d7.jpg&h=7d6ca13e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/212302_f61abc6999d8955a6b38c2c4504eb14d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F212302_f61abc6999d8955a6b38c2c4504eb14d.jpg&h=425f3d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 已係ps 較sharp左"},{"pid":"f29bef24023c1fcc2ab03b538ceaef803163a37a","tid":162740,"uid":45328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚"},{"pid":"c9a78be829fb866cf6ef84954d2e97cbf6c887a8","tid":162740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"冇問題呀"},{"pid":"5bb1c9574bae0c4ff49efbae61b7d29e32f117a1","tid":162740,"uid":88683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏"},{"pid":"88e021b20269460c3c8ab5ac174fb3479d032d01","tid":162740,"uid":45328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏</blockquote><br />\n放大睇其實sharpness都還可以，之不過你話收到f/16其實畫質會反跌；係，色偏都幾嚴重，介唔介意透露邊度scan? <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Y08xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Y08xa.jpg&h=12afc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢張f/8, 喺尖沙咀Dotwell沖+scan，平價scan黎講算係咁，你不妨拎你呢幾張相條片去試下原筒scan大jpeg或者tiff，叫佢「直出」佢就唔會幫你執任何野，再比較下你之前scan果d；如果港島人可以去彩圖麗，又係平靚正"},{"pid":"415f34d0e08576ded83142a6e6fae434acd89ff8","tid":162740,"uid":88683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏</blockquote><br />\n放大睇其實sharpness都還可以，之不過你話收到f/16其實畫質會反跌；係，色偏都幾嚴重，介唔介意透露邊度scan? <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Y08xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Y08xa.jpg&h=12afc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢張f/8, 喺尖沙咀Dotwell沖+scan，平價scan黎講算係咁，你不妨拎你呢幾張相條片去試下原筒scan大jpeg或者tiff，叫佢「直出」佢就唔會幫你執任何野，再比較下你之前scan果d；如果港島人可以去彩圖麗，又係平靚正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實用菲林機係咪點都冇Dc 咁sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n;我自己係屋企沖掃既 我諗係我沖得唔好 都係頭幾水沖 所以乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔知係邊個步驟影響到個色"},{"pid":"df59f71e474a8c24b1319a211da16d6441202d21","tid":162740,"uid":45328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏</blockquote><br />\n放大睇其實sharpness都還可以，之不過你話收到f/16其實畫質會反跌；係，色偏都幾嚴重，介唔介意透露邊度scan? <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Y08xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Y08xa.jpg&h=12afc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢張f/8, 喺尖沙咀Dotwell沖+scan，平價scan黎講算係咁，你不妨拎你呢幾張相條片去試下原筒scan大jpeg或者tiff，叫佢「直出」佢就唔會幫你執任何野，再比較下你之前scan果d；如果港島人可以去彩圖麗，又係平靚正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實用菲林機係咪點都冇Dc 咁sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n;我自己係屋企沖掃既 我諗係我沖得唔好 都係頭幾水沖 所以乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔知係邊個步驟影響到個色</blockquote><br />\n自己沖負片咁犀利，不過不外乎係溫度/藥水比例/時間，試多幾次就應該ok；如果係掃嘅問題就可能要用個好d嘅software用返個啱嘅color profile；當然唔係啦，scan得好可以sharp到嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491043bed117d0f8f09f357c714f54c197296b95","tid":162740,"uid":88683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏</blockquote><br />\n放大睇其實sharpness都還可以，之不過你話收到f/16其實畫質會反跌；係，色偏都幾嚴重，介唔介意透露邊度scan? <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Y08xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Y08xa.jpg&h=12afc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢張f/8, 喺尖沙咀Dotwell沖+scan，平價scan黎講算係咁，你不妨拎你呢幾張相條片去試下原筒scan大jpeg或者tiff，叫佢「直出」佢就唔會幫你執任何野，再比較下你之前scan果d；如果港島人可以去彩圖麗，又係平靚正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實用菲林機係咪點都冇Dc 咁sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n;我自己係屋企沖掃既 我諗係我沖得唔好 都係頭幾水沖 所以乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔知係邊個步驟影響到個色</blockquote><br />\n自己沖負片咁犀利，不過不外乎係溫度/藥水比例/時間，試多幾次就應該ok；如果係掃嘅問題就可能要用個好d嘅software用返個啱嘅color profile；當然唔係啦，scan得好可以sharp到嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打真係唔覺我啲相唔多sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試下揾下其他相<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inPzDb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinPzDb9.jpg&h=dc90048a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似依張咁 較sharp左都係咁 係咪我唔中焦既問題<br />\n<br />\n其實如果係scanner既問題 我認命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9eaf6e61ad3a3d969a16641a3f2bdd9240e8d4","tid":162740,"uid":45328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏</blockquote><br />\n放大睇其實sharpness都還可以，之不過你話收到f/16其實畫質會反跌；係，色偏都幾嚴重，介唔介意透露邊度scan? <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Y08xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Y08xa.jpg&h=12afc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢張f/8, 喺尖沙咀Dotwell沖+scan，平價scan黎講算係咁，你不妨拎你呢幾張相條片去試下原筒scan大jpeg或者tiff，叫佢「直出」佢就唔會幫你執任何野，再比較下你之前scan果d；如果港島人可以去彩圖麗，又係平靚正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實用菲林機係咪點都冇Dc 咁sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n;我自己係屋企沖掃既 我諗係我沖得唔好 都係頭幾水沖 所以乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔知係邊個步驟影響到個色</blockquote><br />\n自己沖負片咁犀利，不過不外乎係溫度/藥水比例/時間，試多幾次就應該ok；如果係掃嘅問題就可能要用個好d嘅software用返個啱嘅color profile；當然唔係啦，scan得好可以sharp到嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打真係唔覺我啲相唔多sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試下揾下其他相<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inPzDb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinPzDb9.jpg&h=dc90048a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似依張咁 較sharp左都係咁 係咪我唔中焦既問題<br />\n<br />\n其實如果係scanner既問題 我認命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用邊部scanner?"},{"pid":"c1ff429b057b066aaf95437d0c8ea464ae7f00c7","tid":162740,"uid":88683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺邊度沖+scan? 建議你轉一轉地方<br />\n或者影一筒正片就試得最清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有色偏</blockquote><br />\n放大睇其實sharpness都還可以，之不過你話收到f/16其實畫質會反跌；係，色偏都幾嚴重，介唔介意透露邊度scan? <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Y08xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Y08xa.jpg&h=12afc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢張f/8, 喺尖沙咀Dotwe